, video moderation, and UGC moderation for social media; supply chain and operations management; digital transformation and automation; finance and accounting outsourcing; creator economy support; healthcare litigation support solutions; and IT support and custom development services. Additionally, the company offers intelligent OCR menu processing; and ITLytics, a data analytics platform that integrates with any data source to deliver actionable insights. It serves banking and financial, telecom, insurance, airlines, consumer durables, FMCG, retail, e-commerce, travel, and hospitality industries. The company was incorporated in 2008 and is headquartered in Navi Mumbai, India."}}